data.description: NO HOA, NO DEED RESTRICTIONS, ON A CUL DE SAC. THIS WILL MAKE A GREAT FIRST OR SECOND HOME OR AN INVESTMENT. THIS PROPERTY  FEATURES 3 BEDROOM SPLIT BEDROOM PLAN, 2 BATHS, A LARGE LIVING SPACE, LARGE KITCHEN WITH PLENTY OF CABINETS FOR STORAGE, KITCHEN BOAST AN ISLAND AND LARGE BREAKFAST NOOK. NEWER APPLIANCE. NEWER CIELING FANS THROUGHOUT THE HOME, TILE IN ALL THE RIGHT PLACES. PRIMARY BEDROOM IS LARGE IN SIZE AND FEATURES NICE DOUBLE WALK IN CLOSETS, ENSUITED BATHROOM THAT HAS DUAL SINKS, STANDUP SHOWER, PRIMARTY BEDROOM HAS SLIDING GLASS DOORS THAT LEAD OUT TO THE BACK SCREENED IN LANAI WITH NO REAR OR SIDE NEIGHBORS YOU CAN SIT ON YOUR BACK PATIO AND ENJOY NATURE AT ITS FINEST. THIS PROPERTY HAS EXTRA PARKING PAD IN FRONT AND A SLAB IN BACK YARD TO PUT YOUR RV/CAMPER, PLUS A 14 X 24 NEW SINGLE CAR GARAGE/SHED/WORKSHOP/TINY HOME/ THAT HAS A SINGLE CAR GARAGE DOOR AND A SIDE DOUBLE DOOR ENTERANCE, WITH A LOFT AND STILL UNDER WARRANTY, THIS IS WAITING FOR YOU TO CREATE YOUR OWN VISION. ALL OF THIS SITS ON JUST UNDER A 1/2 ACRE, PARTIALLY FENCED YARD WAITING FOR YOU TO CALL YOUR OWN. PROPERTY FEELS LIKE YOUR MILES AWAY FROM EVERYTHING BUT YOU ARE WITHIN MINUTES TO STORES, RESTURANTS, SHOPS, HOSPITALS, FAMOUS WEEKI WACHEE SPRINGS/MERMAIDS AND SUNCOAST PARKWAY WHICH MAKES A QUICK TRIP TO TAMPA AND NEARBY AIRPORTS.
